{"tid":862075,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"原來同兔仔洗澡是好危險! 🐰🌟🌟","createTime":"2018-10-14T14:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T16:02:18.000Z","uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"96fe1258bb72aa35dfde4d8d97564e203547e76f","tid":862075,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T14:51:27.000Z","msg":"兔子很愛乾淨，會自動自己清理洗澡。同兔仔洗澡是很危險的，會令牠精神創傷，嚇怕到呆和僵硬，經常這樣會心臟病發死。但是，有一個例外：就是如果牠們有poopy butthole, 可以給牠們一個butt bath, 但不要用手直接拉牠們的糞便，因為會連皮拉出來。要用水浸到牠們的肛門和腳然後就可以慢慢清理。兔仔是被捕獵的動物，在大自然內是每個捕獵者的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚的。<br />\n<br />\n如果主人試過幫兔子洗澡，可能見過兔子用後腳站起來，左右手上下方向擦。這時候兔子其實不是同你玩水，這個姿態是代表不高興，想主人不要理會牠。以下video可看到主人給兔子洗澡時，兔子在3:26被嚇暈：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6zkyjfOq36g&d=GeeNnGMGm3oQLpY9yNG5uZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=3fc3c6a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">N.B.: </span>實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>參觀然後領養</strong></span>，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=GeeNnGMGm3oQLpY9yNG5uZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=08d0768c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a>"},{"pid":"e9fa6e3a5cfeccbc971a8e00803c53cb40907024","tid":862075,"uid":46943,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T15:42:52.000Z","msg":"紅燒免頭安全啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad30ebd96073826d873da1cc0a05dd8f00e6bfd","tid":862075,"uid":60292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e9fa6e3a5cfeccbc971a8e00803c53cb40907024","tid":862075,"uid":46943,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T15:42:52.000Z","msg":"紅燒免頭安全啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T15:48:40.000Z","msg":"怎麼可以吃兔兔"},{"pid":"5600fed1ed3bcf6dce277fa54fbc3c4ca3b4a52f","tid":862075,"uid":61655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:01:56.000Z","msg":"唔記得邊到睇過養兔係最舒緩主人情緒之首"},{"pid":"c3499f9b1bff396591172b9b1aa9c1385a3b68aa","tid":862075,"uid":201237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T16:02:18.000Z","msg":"兔兔那麼可愛"}]}